social_posts.post_text: Yeehawed to some country music yesterday
8 weeks with my precious little muffin. Does this mean we’re officially out of the newborn phase?😢
Millie in her pool float is now my new favorite thing
Millie went to her first St. Paddy’s party. Huge fan of green beer.

Doggy, dad and daughter approved. I’m not one to suggest a lot of baby products because I’m a brand new mom trying to figure it out myself but The Glider Plus from @nurture_and is the best decision we made for Millie’s nursery. So comfortable, power recline, has a USB port for phone charging, stain-resistant fabric, swivels and glides and is just the best chair I’ve ever met🙌🏼 #madeforsharedmoments
Happy Easter! 🤍 I have a feeling every holiday is going to feel a little more special from here on out.
17 hrs in Tampa for Taylor Swift and some girl time🫶🏻
10/10 weekend
A weekend with my mom and my daughter🥹💗
Millie does Key West Songwriters Festival
Four months of Millie. Her big blue eyes, precious cheeks and huge personality from day one have brought me a type of joy I’ve never felt. I never wanna know a day without you Camilla Reece.
My very first Mother’s Day as a mama🥹 I’m so grateful to have this precious baby girl in my arms. Happy Mother’s Day to all the moms in my life💗

Freedom isn’t free. Spent the past four days celebrating friends’ birthdays and getting to raise this little baby in the USA. That’s only possible because of the men and women who gave their lives for this country and we are so thankful🇺🇸
Girls night out= Guys night in with the babies💙
FIVE months of Millie. She gets funnier every day and I still can’t believe this little blue eyed angel is mine. #fivemonthsold
Millie’s the happiest when her daddy is singing to her. And now she has her very own song out in the world! Check out “Happy Hour Drinks” by @rickyyoungmusic anywhere you listen💗💗
You’re good at everything you do but I really think you were born for this role, @rickyyoungmusic 💙Happy first Father’s Day!

Ricky & Millie have daddy daughter time every morning and today they walked the beach just after sunrise. They were lucky enough to meet @mr.ippster who was flying his drone and now they have the greatest video with special guest turtles, sharks and manatees. What a place to live🙌🏼 #jupiter
Bffs since second grade now our babies are playing together🥹
American baby🇺🇸
Woke up this morning with a 6 month old. Millie is the best part of every day and somehow it just keeps getting better and better. What a ray of sunshine. I love you my Milliegirl☀️
Dance then jump OR ELSE!!!
My old besties met my new, tiny best friend this weekend. Plus, we found out we’re adding a baby boy to the mix! (Paige, not me)
7 months of Millie. You can’t convince me it gets better than this. There’s just no way.
Happy birthday to the best guy and the very best dad. 10 years in and it was my favorite year with you yet🤍

My birthday is tomorrow and all I want is for you and anyone you know with kids to subscribe to our new kids YouTube channel. It’s called Super Shellz and it has been the most fun project to produce and write for. If you have kids between 2-7 yrs old that love laughing, seeing cool ocean animals, learning a little (shh we won’t tell them that part) and listening to really fun music then this is for you/them! Ricky didn’t originally plan to be a big character in the show, just the silly guy at the end that sang some music about the episode but McCoy the Beach Cowboy brings about as many laughs as the hysterical Super Shellz (@brookenix12) and her cute/hilarious kiddos. What I’m saying is, if you need a little break from Ms Rachel, Blippi or the likes, check out @supershellz!
That’s what happens when you kiss a boy in a Gamecocks hat #rolltide #7months
🎂My mom came to town to celebrate her birthday with lil Millie
A night with the ladies and T.I.
6th Anniversary, best one yet. Started it at @eauspa and ended with the sweetest little angel in the world.
Happiest wedding day to @nikki_guidish! So sad to miss the big day but so glad we got to celebrate you before you left! 🇮🇹👰‍♀️
Pumpkin patchin’ 🎃
Long Live Cowgirl Millie
Couldn’t let your feeds have other babies in pumpkins but not Millie, right?!! 🎃 #pumpkinbaby #babyinapumpkin
A little Halloween roundup 🎃

social_posts.post_text: The most beautiful, oceanside Friendsgiving there ever was! A five course, barefoot dining experience with some of my best gal pals to kick off holiday season💛 Thank you to @marriottharborbeach and Chef Marco for the perfect night and coastal Thanksgiving inspired meal. If you’re anywhere near Fort Lauderdale grab some friends or family and plan a night before it ends November 20th! #friendsgiving #marriotbonvoy #harbourbeachlife
